These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, trike
1. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the accountant is on the right of the paramedic##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | juice    |
| Job           | paramedic | accountant |
| Nationality   | nigerian       | argentine  |
| Transport     | roller      | trike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, cabbage
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, ambient
2 different pets are kept: snake, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, tram
1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | cabbage | zucchini |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | ambient         |
| Pet           | rat     | snake         |
| Transport     | tram    | bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, puzzles
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, firefighter
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, salsa
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, van
1. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the person driving the van is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | puzzles          | reading |
| Job           | firefighter | social-worker     |
| Music-Genre   | rock            | salsa         |
| Transport     | van         | roller   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, comedy
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
2 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish
1. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the frog##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | lemonade   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | zombie |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | r&b |
| Pet           | frog | goldfish    |

