.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, avocado
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, salsa
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, helicopter
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person eating nectarine is the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of ambient is the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | 7up     | soy-milk |
| Food          | avocado   | nectarine |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | ambient     |
| Transport     | subway | helicopter     |

 